Expressing myself and finding friends by coding.

kaixin.py-samples
kaixin.py-samples is a step-by-step tutorial. Follow this tutorial to learn how kaixin.py work.

step1-minimal
  A minimal WSGI application in kaixin.py way.
step2-urlmapping
  Mapping URL to modules.
step3-auth
  Add authentication, verity a token in query string.